You are creating your own social network and need to turn words into hashtags.

The code takes a word as input.

Task

Complete the hashtag() function to return the input word starting with the hashtag symbol (#). Then display the result on the screen.

---

#taking a word as input
word = str(input())

def hashtag(word):
    #complete the function body
    new_hashtag = "#" + word
    return new_hashtag

#display the result
print(hashtag(word))
